description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, Ross Tucker calls in to discuss the rules for NFL players and gambling. How much of a topic was it when he was playing? Josh Duhamel invites DP and the guys to his wedding. And Nick Wright reacts to Aaron Rodgers deciding to stay in Green Bay.
